'''Anégrée Freese''' is a [[football (soccer)]] club from [[Central African Republic]] based in [[Bangui]].
The team plays in the [[Central African Republic League]].<ref>{{cite web|title=futbolparalospueblos|url=http://futbolparalospueblos.blogspot.it/2013/11/por-fin-ha-comenzado-la-competicion-en.html|work=lospueblos|accessdate=25 March 2013}}</ref>
==Stadium== Currently the team plays at the 35000 capacity [[Barthelemy Boganda Stadium]].
