'''Derna Stadium''' ({{lang-ar|ملعب درنة}}) is a multi-use [[stadium]] in [[Derna, Libya|Derna]], [[Libya]].  It is currently used mostly for [[football (soccer)|football]] matches and is the home ground of [[Darnes]] & [[Afriqi Darnah|Afriqi]].  The stadium holds 7,000 people.<ref>[http://www.worldstadiums.com/africa/countries/libya.shtml World Stadiums - Stadiums in Libya]</ref>

