{{Infobox Stadium | stadium_name = Estádio Municipal Santos Diniz | image = | location = [[N'dalatando]], [[Angola]] | coordinates = | broke_ground = | opened = | renovated = | closed = | demolished = | owner = | operator = | construction_cost = | architect = | former_names = | tenants = U.R. Cuanza Norte | seating_capacity = 5,000 }}
'''Estádio Municipal Santos Diniz''' is a [[football (soccer)|football]] [[stadium]] in [[N'dalatando]], [[Cuanza Norte Province]], [[Angola]]. The stadium holds 5,000.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.girabola.com/?p=estadio&id=37|title=Estádio Municipal Santos Diniz|website=www.girabola.com|access-date=17 Jun 2018}}</ref>
In 2013, the stadium was the home ground of local club [[Porcelana Futebol Clube do Cazengo]] in the [[2013 Girabola|first division]].<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.angop.ao/angola/pt_pt/noticias/desporto/2013/1/5/Estadio-Santos-Diniz-restaurado-para-Girabola,907f2533-dd31-4d96-abc2-c30b5cb3ed5d.html |title=Estádio Santos Diniz restaurado para Girabola |publisher=ANGOP Angolan News Agency |accessdate= 17 Jun 2018 |language=pt}}</ref>
In 2018, the stadium has been the home ground of local club União Recreativo do Cuanza Norte in the [[2018 Gira Angola|second division]].
