{{Refimprove|date=April 2008}}
'''Pixbo Wallenstam Innebandyklubb''', also known as Redfox or Pixbo IBK, is one of the most successful [[floorball]] clubs in the world. It is based in [[Mölnlycke]], [[Västra Götaland]] and is widely recognized as the best floorball club in [[Sweden]], more specifically, in the [[Swedish Super League (men's floorball)|Swedish Super League]]. Pixbo IBK has captured various awards, such as the Swedish Championships (2002, 2003), the European Championship (Now the EuroFloorball Cup) (2004), and the Swedish Ligacup (2008).

